gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bucks 118, Magic 114
gameRecap.excerpt: The Bucks defeated the Magic, 118-114. Giannis Antetokounmpo tallied his tenth 35+ point game of the year with 37 points, 10 rebounds, and six assists as Damian Lillard added 24 points, five rebounds, and eight assists. Franz Wagner (29 points, six rebounds, six assists) and Paolo Banchero (23 points, seven rebounds, four assists) led Orlando in defeat. The Bucks win their sixth in a row to improve to 21-7 on the year and the Magic have now lost four in a row and move to 16-11.
